      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/world/middleeast/strait-hormuz-open-iran-lebanon-ceasefire.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统和伊朗发表声明旨在提高人们对航道安全的信心，但航运专家表示风险仍然存在。]]></description>
